& [DeepResearchPriorityGateApplication] is triggered
  + [curiosity_signal] is repair as possible strength increase
  + [resolution_gap] is low_resolution_theorem_boundary
  + [proof_obligation_link] is determine whether repair upgrades local propagation to a stronger proof system or reintroduces branching whose cost must be counted
