  + [admission_status] is boundary_only
  + [first_missing_feature] is no_polynomial_bound_on_repair_conflict_trace_size_for_hard_sat_instances

& [DevelopedUnderstanding] is proposition adjustment
  + [old_shape] is repair may rescue local propagation from bounded-width weakness
  + [new_shape] is repair must be counted as proof search and clause derivation; if it learns clauses it enters resolution/CDCL proof complexity
  + [meaning_gained] is repair can strengthen the operator's proof-system home from bounded-width local consistency toward resolution/CDCL, but the central obstruction simply moves to proof-size and conflict-count bounds
  + [route_status] is not_blocked_as_a_scoped_model_but_blocked_as_solution_route
  + [lock_mass_change] is reduced_ambiguity_not_problem_lock

& [NextBoundedMotion] is follow-up
